Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction flows with the rhythm of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark stains are rinsed clean and exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case in the big house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smash with the deductive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, Pops and I are invited by Sonoko and head for her villa in Karuizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On our way, our things together with the car sink into the river
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the water level rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We end up being able to spend the night at a house in the remote mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that we finally manage to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the owner of that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Iwao Akashi dies in has room upstalrs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicious Spicy Curry" Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Yamamura from the Gunma Prefectural Poltce Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh~~excuse me...\NI'd like to ask you a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes... what can I do for you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traces of something having been wrapped areund your father's wrists
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... is that true...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had been tied up by someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think those are traces of rubber bands...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father had a habit of bunching everything and anything up with rubber bands,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and always had rubber bands round both his wrists...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you thought...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a lot of rubber bands under his pillow, so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there any thing else that you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like having seen someone suspicious around your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or having heard strange sounds or volces...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I went in front of that room the first time I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the man weeping, "Uuugh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard him crying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably crying after deciding to commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, didn't you see anything else in that room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he wiped his mouth with it while eating curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because there was a little curry on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akashi didn't go to the dentist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why he was bleeding from his mouth was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,probably because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, sonny, what's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... So, it's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had his tooth pulled out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his gums would've started to close like the not yet opened bud of a flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his gums are still opened with no signs of closing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither are there signs of blood that would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the opening of the gum having dried up or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he just got his tooth pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the other teeth around it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means that whatever he was clenching with all his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between his teeth was pulled out with great force...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get the picture... of this trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this trick is what I think it is, at should be somewhere in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come it's nowhere in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This half-eaten curry over rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there wasn't any poison in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so shall we have them put it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... you want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop it!\NY-You gotta be kidding? Hey, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Found it... This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that... a tooth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, a human's tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed Iwao created
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,created his own alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that person is Hirohito Akashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now that I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to get everyone to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and start the usual\NSleeping Kogoro deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What shall we do with this tooth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we better report this to Officer Yamamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O... Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn!...What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I figured out the case and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't use the voice changer to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the truth of the case to anyone in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would write but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but with this sprained wrist I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only if they'd solve it themselves somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My only hope is that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(So, what I think is...)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the members here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, just where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(I,I've lost my voice!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no?! You mean you lost your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were told not to talk because you'd lose your voice, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is plain to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time that Mr. Iwao Akashi passed away in his bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around 7:30 p m. Ran, Conan, Sonoko and Hirohito, who were in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we all have an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a bath, but have no motive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had no way of getting the rope ready either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover... an hour before we discovered the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the light of the bedroom was on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when we discovered the body, it was turned off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it this is suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iwao turned off the light of the room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then committed suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'd advise you to stop investigating right now and go on back to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is homicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a trick to make it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is Iwao's adopted son, Hirohito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how should I accuse him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, although this is going to be a bit bothersome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, just what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he gesturing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ripe crackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,14 pieces of rice crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(No, no...)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crack, one... four?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Close, close!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,crack code one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crack this code... once and for all... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Yes, yes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what is there to crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? That curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was spicy but good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(No, no)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's not it... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:50.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The old man upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...3?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a little over 33 already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran was born when I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the amount of curry we all ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirohito, his father, Sonoko and I had one serving each,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but dad ate 3 servings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Right, right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's wrong with that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you and your group just happened to come by
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to this house tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, Hirohito usually lives here only with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are just the two of you here, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, curry enough for 7 people is a bit too much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for just two people living together, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would surprise the Indians in India too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mentioned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must like curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually love curry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made quite a lot because\NI usually invite the students
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I've become friends, over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really seem to like the curry I make...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad there was nobody at the tennis court today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because it rained...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the tooth... curry... no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Bull's eye!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That after a tooth is pulled out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eating something too spicy is not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember when you had your decayed tooth pulled out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the dentist told you so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, then it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your father had his tooth pulled out\N2 or 3 days ago, didn't you, Mr. Akashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I had no idea that he had his tooth pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Yamamura, could I speak to you for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the coroner is here checking on the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he says that Iwao's tooth seems to have been pulled out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just a while ago, not 2 or 3 days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the tooth that was pulled out seems to have been found in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to have been found for some reason in the half-eaten curry dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must've been very tough meat in the curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the teeth near the tooth that had come off all seemed to be shaky too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think such tough meat was in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was eating curry, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You want me to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring the tied part of the necktie around behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bring the end of the necktie to the front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while biting on the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Bingo!)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would eventually get tired
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then he'd be strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His tooth probably flew into the curry dish at that time because of the impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his mouth is blocked with the rope, he probably couldn't yell out either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that voice that I heard back then was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not him weeping, but him groaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were no traces of the rope by his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the handkerchief with the curry on it was near the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, {The handkerchief with the curry on r14 was negwthe corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was made to bite the handkerchief together with the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then traces of the rope wouldn't be left around his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, his hands weren't tied when he was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he grabs the rope with both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he can free his mouth so he could've shouted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Somebody help!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bedroom light that was on an hour and a half ago, was turned off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the corpse was found, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All during that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nobody went to that room, so how could the light have been turned off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't play around with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both his wrists were tied with the string of the light fixture in a bow tie
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the edge of the string
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was connected to the string
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when he becomes exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the rope will pull away from his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his body will slide down choking his neck, and at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the string of the light fixture will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The string that is tied to his wrists will untie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the body will be in the exact position as we found at!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the narrow lines that were found on Mr. Iwao Akashi's wrists
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were marks that were left from his wrists being tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But these light fixtures have three levels
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and unless you pull the string 3 times like Conan just did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it won't get dark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pulling just once would only turn off the fluorescent light on the outer part,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pulling the string twice will still leave the miniature light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the brightness is adjusted to the 2nd level and the miniature light is loosened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then pulling on the string just once will turn off the light right then and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...But, is it possible to untie it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, this part that is tied to make the string longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to tie the hand of someone who is struggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would be impossible to do so while the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this knot would have to be untied once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this looks to be a complicated knot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is called "Tegusu Musubi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way a fishing line is tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A slippery line has to be tied like this or it'll get untied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!That's why Hirohito's wife went
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to know how to tie the string of the light fixture firmly in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why was the bedroom string different then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The string in the bedroom was tied into a regular knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's why the string of the light fixture of the bedroom was shorter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was unable to untie the knot, so he had to cut it using scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the string was tied into a regular knot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the killer didn't know how to tie it fishing line style!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right Mr. Hirohito Akashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick you used goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the curry to\NIwao's bedroom upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was eating the curry, you probably covered his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the handkerchief from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tied him up with the light fixture string that you cut with the scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After putting the loop of the rope around his neck, you made him bite the rope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,partway along with the hankerchief, and left him suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you threatened him saying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that if he lets go of the rope from his mouth he would choke to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally all you had to do was tie the string of the light fixture that both of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his hands were tied with onto the string of the light fixture... and wallah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you make somebody go to the bedroom to pick up his curry dish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You warn that person saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the light is on he's still eating so don't go into the room."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first ask the person to go get the plate 10 somewhat minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after you bring the curry to his room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he most likely is still holding the rope in has mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you ask that person to go and get the plate again after a while
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,goes in and encounters the dead bedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you were with us right through in the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you most definitely have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, are you saying that Hirohito was at the tennis court
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the rain to invite someone to witness his alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He deliberately made curry for a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means if we didn't come here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even if you all didn't come here today,\NI was going to kill him tongiht...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...It's true that today is the anniversary of my wife's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife was found lying on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Lying on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was when I went out to work at a court in Tokyo on a rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father suddenly woke my wife who was asleep with a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made her go shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told her that he wanted to eat mushroom rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should've refused, but she didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She walked with unsteady steps over to a supermarket about 3 kilometers away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way back, just as expected, fell to the ground and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that's no reason for you to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to kill the day after my wife's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umaware that I was behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,father was mumbling the following words towards the altar of my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear... she finally broke down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time I wish he'd get himself a healthier wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A toy that is more durable like Hirohito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O... Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You mentioned that you were adopted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, until I heard him say that,\NI believed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,thinking that his being selfish was proof
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he acknowledged me as his real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... We built a house in the forest and began living here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my father, wife and I, because of my father's selfishness saying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he wanted to live apart from the rest of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course the same goes for the string of the light fixture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly lengthened the string of the light fixture of his room
